title: Malik Aitbar Khan wins PP-5 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Pakistan Muslim League (N) candidate, Malik Aitbar Khan has won the election for Punjab Assembly constituency PP-5, Attock-V by securing 46,665 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Independent candidate, Malik Jamshed Altaf who bagged 43,620 votes.
The votersâ€™ turn-out remained 53.60%.
